description=Military Ponchos: Reloaded is a complete overhaul of the popular Military Poncho’s mod by Akyet, expanding its variety and refining its gameplay balance. This update introduces a wide range of new camouflage patterns, including M81 Woodland, Tigerstripe, 3 Color Desert, 6 Color Desert, and Flecktarn, alongside bold new solid color options like Red, White, and Blue—in addition to the classic Green, Black, and Yellow.The ponchos have been rebalanced for better gameplay consistency, now providing 20% bite and 25% scratch protection, making them a viable lightweight outer layer for survivors. Loot distribution has also been overhauled, ensuring all variants can be found in diverse locations throughout the world, making these military ponchos more accessible and immersive. Compatible with Build 42!
